# BitProtector

Distributed File Mirror and Integrity Protection System.

Monitors files across redundant storage, detects corruption,
and automatically recovers from mirror copies.

## Quick Start

    bitprotector drives add mybackup /primary/path /secondary/path
    bitprotector files track <drive-id> /primary/path/to/file.txt
    bitprotector integrity check all
    bitprotector status

## Service

    sudo systemctl enable --now bitprotector

The web UI is served directly by the backend at:

    https://localhost:8443/

## Package Build

Build the frontend before running `cargo deb`:

    cd frontend && npm ci && npm run build && cd ..
    cargo deb

## Configuration

Edit /etc/bitprotector/config.toml to configure the server.
